USSD menu for farmer
=================
# Add product
- category
- product name
- quantity
- unit price
- Minimum order

**API endpoint for adding a new product**

`POST /products`

**Arguments**
- `"name":string` name of the product
- `"category":string` category that the product belong to
- `"price":string` unit price of the product
- `"description":string` description of the product 

**Response**
- `201 Created` on success

```json
{
	"name": "banana",
	"category": "fruits",
	"price": "200",
	""description: "Green bananas"
}
```
## List all categories of products

**API endpoint for getting all categories**

`GET /products/categories`

# See products categories
- grains
- fruits
- vegetables
- poultry
- dairy

**Response**

- `200 OK` on success

```json
{
	`"name": "fruits"`,
	`"description": all fruits`
}
```

